Ventra Management Inc, an over thecounter company, said it acquired Joint Venture Leasing Inc for60 mln Venture shares, valued at 3.6 mln dlrs.    Joint Venture was organized in September 1986 to establishleasing joint ventures with manufacturers and vendors ofcomputer equipment.    As a result of the acquisition and Joint Venture's backlog,Ventra said it expects 1987 sales to be 30 mln dlrs with netprofits of 1.5 mln dlrs.    Ventra was organized in September 1986 and completed apublic offering of 30 mln shares in January 1987. Reuter&#3;